headline: US Bancorp Says It Believes Exec Dolan Was On Plane That Crashed
summary: US Bancorp said Monday that it believed its vice chair and chief administration officer, Terrance Dolan, was on a plane that crashed in Minnesota on Saturday.

headline: The Magnificent 7, automakers, Moderna, Warner Bros. Discovery, U.S. Bancorp: Stocks to watch today
summary: Stocks fell on Monday after the Wall Street Journal reported that President Donald Trump has pushed his team to be more aggressive on tariffs in recent days. The S&P 500 fell 1.3%, the Nasdaq Composite 2.2%, and the Dow Jones Industrial Average 0.6% as of 9:54 a.m. EDT.
